author: Alan Fram, Associated Press
title: GOP lawmaker obtains Planned Parenthood videos
text: Photo: Jacquelyn Martin, AP FILE - In this Oct. 8, 2015, photo, Rep. Jason Chaffetz, R-Utah, attends a news conference on Capitol Hill in Washington. Anti-abortion activists have given Congress lengthy, unedited videos they recorded showing Planned Parenthood officials discussing their retrieval of fetal tissue, Chaffetz said Wednesday, Oct. 14. FILE - In this Oct. 8, 2015, photo, Rep. Jason Chaffetz, R-Utah,... WASHINGTON (AP) — Anti-abortion activists have given Congress lengthy, unedited videos they recorded showing Planned Parenthood officials discussing their retrieval of fetal tissue, a Republican House committee chairman said Wednesday.
